{
"#name"
:
{
"claw"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI 消息机器人"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI message bot"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw <SUBCMD>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"自托管 AI Agent 网关，将 LLM 接入微信、飞书、Telegram 等即时通讯平台。\n监听 IM 消息并触发本地 AI Agent 执行自主任务，支持通过 `x agent request` 调用\nclaude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli 等多种 AI 引擎，\n每个会话拥有独立 workspace 与持久化上下文记忆。\n"
,
"en"
:
"A self-hosted AI Agent gateway that connects LLMs to WeChat, Feishu, Telegram and other IM platforms.\nListens for IM messages and triggers local AI Agents to execute autonomous tasks,\nsupporting multiple AI engines via `x agent request` (claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli),\nwith independent workspaces and persistent context memory per session.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"使用 'x claw start' 启动网关服务，支持多平台同时运行（如 `x claw start --weixin --telegram`）。\n不指定平台时自动检测已登录的 IM 平台，默认回退到 weixin。\n支持的 IM 平台: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx。\nAI Agent 引擎可通过 'x agent request' 配置切换（如 claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Use 'x claw start' to start the gateway, supports multiple platforms simultaneously (e.g., `x claw start --weixin --telegram`).\nAuto-detects logged-in IM platforms when not specified, with weixin as fallback default.\nSupported IM platforms: weixin, telegram, feishu, qywx.\nAI Agent engine can be switched via 'x agent request' config (e.g. claude, codex, cursor, gemini-cli, opencode, kimi-cli).\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动网关服务（自动检测可用平台）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start gateway service (auto-detect available platform)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw log"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看网关服务日志"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show gateway service log"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Service"
:
[
"start"
,
"stop"
,
"restart"
,
"status"
,
"log"
,
"connect"
,
"disconnect"
]
,
"#subcmd:inner"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"qywx"
,
"agentrequest"
,
"cron"
]
,
"start"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Start Gateway service"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw start [FLAG]"
:
null
}
]
,
"--weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable WeChat platform"
}
}
,
"--telegram"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用 Telegram 平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Telegram platform"
}
}
,
"--feishu"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用飞书平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Feishu platform"
}
}
,
"--qywx"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启用企业微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Enable Qywx (Enterprise WeChat) platform"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"启动时若不指定平台，自动检测已配置并登录的 IM 平台，默认回退到 weixin。\n飞书用户通常先启动单聊: `x claw start --feishu`，然后在飞书中让 Agent 按需连接更多群聊。\n连接指定群聊: `x claw connect feishu:oc_xxx` (群 ID 可通过 `x feishu group ls` 查看)\n连接所有群聊: `x claw connect feishu:groups`\n"
,
"en"
:
"If no platform is specified, auto-detects configured and logged-in IM platforms, falling back to weixin by default.\nFeishu users typically start with single chat first: `x claw start --feishu`, then ask the Agent in Feishu to connect more groups on demand.\nConnect a specific group: `x claw connect feishu:oc_xxx` (group ID via `x feishu group ls`)\nConnect all groups: `x claw connect feishu:groups`\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动网关服务（自动检测可用平台）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start gateway service (auto-detect available platform)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start --weixin --telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动微信和 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start WeChat and Telegram gateway services"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start --feishu"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动飞书网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start Feishu gateway service"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start --qywx --telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动企业微信和 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start Qywx and Telegram gateway services"
}
]
}
,
