:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停止网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Stop Gateway service"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw stop [FLAG]"
:
null
}
]
,
"--weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停用微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Disable WeChat platform"
}
}
,
"--telegram"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停用 Telegram 平台"
,
"en"
:
"Disable Telegram platform"
}
}
,
"--feishu"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停用飞书平台"
,
"en"
:
"Disable Feishu platform"
}
}
,
"--qywx"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停用企业微信平台"
,
"en"
:
"Disable Qywx (Enterprise WeChat) platform"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"停止时若不指定平台，自动断开所有已激活的连接并停止后台服务。\n飞书单聊和群聊是独立管理的，停止单聊不会自动断开已连接的群聊。\n"
,
"en"
:
"If no platform is specified, disconnects all active connections and stops background services.\nFeishu single chat and group chats are managed independently; stopping single chat does not auto-disconnect linked groups.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw stop"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop gateway service"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw stop --weixin --telegram"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止微信和 Telegram 网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop WeChat and Telegram gateway services"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw stop --feishu"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 停止飞书网关服务"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Stop Feishu gateway service"
}
]
}
,
