,
"status"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看网关服务状态"
,
"en"
:
"Show gateway service status"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw status"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw status"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看网关服务状态"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show gateway service status"
}
]
}
,
"log"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看网关服务日志（按时间线排序）"
,
"en"
:
"Show gateway service log (sorted by timeline)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw log [--all]"
:
null
}
]
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"从头开始显示所有日志内容"
,
"en"
:
"Show all log content from the beginning"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"日志包含所有 IM 平台的消息处理和心跳记录。\n默认显示最新日志流，使用 --all 查看完整历史。\n日志按时间戳排序，支持多行日志条目（如 Agent 输出）。\n心搏日志带有 [HB] 前缀，便于区分。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Logs include message processing and heartbeat records for all IM platforms.\nShows latest log stream by default, use --all for complete history.\nLogs are sorted by timestamp, supporting multi-line entries (e.g., Agent output).\nHeartbeat logs are prefixed with [HB] for easy identification.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw log"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看网关服务最新日志"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show latest gateway service log"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw log --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看所有日志内容（从头开始）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all log content from the beginning"
}
]
}
,
"connect"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"连接指定 IM 平台及会话，激活消息监听通道。支持同时连接多个平台。"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to IM platform(s) and activate message listener channel. Supports multiple platforms at once."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw connect <IM>..."
:
null
}
,
{
"x claw connect --ls"
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"IM 平台标识，可指定多个。格式为 `im` 或 `im:chatid`。\nweixin、telegram、qywx 直接写名称即可；feishu 需要指定 chatid，如 `feishu:groups` 或 `feishu:oc_xxx`。\n"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform identifier, multiple allowed. Format is `im` or `im:chatid`.\nweixin, telegram, qywx can be used directly; feishu requires chatid, e.g. `feishu:groups` or `feishu:oc_xxx`.\n"
}
}
,
"--ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出当前已激活的连接"
,
"en"
:
"List currently activated connections"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"连接前会自动确保对应 IM 的后台服务已启动（如飞书机器人服务、微信消息订阅等）。连接后会自动启动对应的 IM 后台服务，断开会自动停止。"
,
"en"
:
"Automatically ensures the corresponding IM background service is started before connecting. The background service is auto-started on connect and stopped on disconnect."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"连接飞书群时，chatid 格式为 oc_ 开头的群 ID。可通过 `x feishu group ls` 查看可用群列表及其 ID。连接前需先确保飞书应用已配置完成（x feishu init）。"
,
"en"
:
"When connecting to a Feishu group, the chatid is the group ID starting with oc_. Use `x feishu group ls` to list available groups and their IDs. Make sure Feishu app is configured first (x feishu init)."
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"查看当前活跃连接：`x claw connect --ls`"
,
"en"
:
"View active connections with `x claw connect --ls`"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw connect weixin telegram feishu:groups"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 同时连接微信、Telegram 和飞书所有群聊"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Connect to WeChat, Telegram, and all Feishu groups at once"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw connect feishu:oc_xxx"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 连接飞书指定群聊（oc_xxx 为群 ID）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Connect to a Feishu group (oc_xxx is the group ID)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw connect weixin"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 连接微信"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Connect to WeChat"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw connect --ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有已激活的连接"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all activated connections"
}
]
}
,
"disconnect"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"断开指定 IM 平台及会话的连接，停止对应的消息监听。支持同时断开多个平台。"
,
"en"
:
"Disconnect from IM platform(s) and stop the message listener. Supports multiple platforms at once."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw disconnect <IM>..."
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"IM 平台标识，可指定多个。格式与 connect 一致：`im` 或 `im:chatid`。\n省略 chatid 时断开该平台的所有连接。\n"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform identifier, multiple allowed. Same format as connect: `im` or `im:chatid`.\nOmitting chatid disconnects all connections for that platform.\n"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw disconnect weixin telegram feishu:groups"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 同时断开微信、Telegram 和飞书所有群聊"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Disconnect from WeChat, Telegram, and all Feishu groups at once"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw disconnect feishu:oc_xxx"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 断开飞书指定群聊连接"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Disconnect from a Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw disconnect weixin"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 断开微信所有连接"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Disconnect from all WeChat connections"
}
]
}
,
"agentrequest"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"向 AI Agent 发送消息请求，触发 Agent 执行指定任务并将结果回复到对应 IM 会话。"
,
"en"
:
"Send a message request to the AI Agent, triggering it to execute a task and reply to the specified IM session."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw agentrequest <IM> <CHATID> <MSG>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"即时通讯平台名称（如 weixin, telegram, feishu）"
,
"en"
:
"IM platform name (e.g., weixin, telegram, feishu)"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"聊天会话 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Chat session ID"
}
}
,
"#3"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要发送的消息内容（会作为 Agent 的输入提示）"
,
"en"
:
"Message content to send (served as the Agent input prompt)"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"此命令可由用户直接调用，也可被 cron 定时任务或其他 Agent 调用。\n调用时会启动一个新的 AI Agent 实例来处理消息，因此 <MSG> 中需明确包含任务目标、工具和输出格式。\n"
,
"en"
:
"This command can be invoked directly by users, cron jobs, or other Agents.\nIt spawns a new AI Agent instance to process the message, so <MSG> should clearly include the goal, tools, and output format.\n"
}
]
}
,
"weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"微信消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"WeChat message query tools"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw weixin <SUBCMD>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Query"
:
[
"get-msg"
,
"unread-count"
,
"recent-msg"
,
"update-offset"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin get-msg 100:200"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 获取第 100 到 200 行的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get messages from line 100 to 200"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin get-msg 50"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 从第 50 行开始获取到文件末尾"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Get messages from line 50 to end of file"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin update-offset 100"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 将微信已读位置更新到第 100 行"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Update WeChat read offset to line 100"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw weixin unread-count"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看微信未读消息数"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show WeChat unread message count"
}
]
,
"get-msg"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按行号范围获取消息"
,
"en"
:
"Get messages by line range"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
"<START>[:<END>]"
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"行号范围（如 100:200）或起始行号"
,
"en"
:
"Line range (e.g., 100:200) or start line"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"结束行号（可选，与起始行号一起使用）"
,
"en"
:
"End line number (optional, used with start line)"
}
}
}
,
"unread-count"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示未读消息数量"
,
"en"
:
"Show unread message count"
}
}
,
"recent-msg"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"显示最新所有未读的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Show all recent unread messages"
}
}
,
"update-offset"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"更新已读位置到指定行号，标记该行及之前的消息为已读"
,
"en"
:
"Update the read offset to the specified line number, marking messages up to that line as read"
